headline: Otis CEO to Speak at Morgan Stanley Conference
summary: Otis Worldwide Corporation (NYSE: OTIS) Chair, CEO & President Judy Marks will participate in a fireside chat at the 13th annual Laguna conference hosted by Morgan Stanley on Friday, September 12, 2025 at 10:00 a.m. PT (1:00 p.m. ET). The presentation will be broadcast live at www.otis.com.
